Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:42.93,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Close our eyes and recall the promises we shared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:50.39,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake off the falling darkness and keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.87,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I lost sight of the future I once had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:10.29,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I still see it from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:15.84,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,My uneasiness welled up over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.93,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow I cut through it and kept moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:32.14,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,The endless march of time announces a new beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:42.78,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,Following my unchanging emotions, I open that sealed door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:48.95,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,My awakening heart rushes forth, to draw the future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:53.75,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how tough the path ahead is, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:04:00.55,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,a beautiful blue sky is waiting for me, so I'm not afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:06.85,lolop,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:50.11,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One day, perhaps the light of love shining in your eyes will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:52.11,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}(Go beyond the time)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:57.79,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is but one dream, of a world rushing toward its doom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.76,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}(Will it be destroyed?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:06.23,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Swallow your hesitation! What do you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:15.25,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chasing these greedy desires, will the future fade away?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:20.84,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was a girl, I dreamed of you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:24.64,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wielding something like unto ancient magic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:28.29,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be by your side as you smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:32.49,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}filled with the strength to smash even the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:36.18,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In my trembling hand, I grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.98,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the courage of a plucked laurel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:43.80,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Relying only on my emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:55.66,loled,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my prayer awakens the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:23.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was ask you to become magical girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:28.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sure, I left out the part about what your real body would be, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you never asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey, as long as you never found out, no harm, no foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, even that Mami girl never realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:51.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what does it matter? You humans can't even find your souls to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There? To you, it's just a lump of neurons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:58.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And down there is just the core of the circulatory system.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:05.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, when you can no longer maintain life, your spirits fade as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:12.05,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that from happening, I gave your soul form, made you able to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:15.92,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make fighting witches at least a little bit safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:18.97,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what gave you the right to do it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naïve about fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:30.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, think of the pain and shock you'd feel if you took a spear to the gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.58,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is true pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.58,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A single blow, and you're unable to even move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:58.43,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to remain standing in your fight with Kyoko only because you blocked out the worst of the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:02.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,BEcause your consciousness isn't directly connected to your body, you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you survived that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:17.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get used to it, you'll be able to block out all pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:22.37,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that'll blunt your reactions, so perhaps you shouldn't get too used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:26.84,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:31.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you took on your fate of battle, you each had a wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been fulfilled, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:37.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.16,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura... You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:05:00.32,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I told people, they never believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.32,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kyubey do such horrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.82,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't think they're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beings like him have no concept of human values.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:14.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All he'll do is describe it as compensation for the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.46,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fair at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:24.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being turned into that just to heal the wounds of someone she loves!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly was a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.72,madoka-dialogue,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,He made the impossible possible. {is -this- where that koyasu rumor came frm?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.92,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Sayaka Miki had cared for him for the rest of her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy would never have played the violin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:45.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, miracles cannot even be purchased with one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet {\i1}he{\fscx40} {\r} sells them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka will never be able to go back, will she.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:58.00,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before. Give up on Sayaka Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.99,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sayaka saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:08.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sayaka wasn't a magical girl, Hitomi and I both would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dion't confuse gratitude and responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.88,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:22.40,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go out of your way to worry about feeling weak or wanting to pay her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.18,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura... Why are you so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.41,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's because I'm no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:45.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I face Kyosuke with my body like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to mope around, silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having a tough time. Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:14.12,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Having some regrets about your new body, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:24.63,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, ever since I got this power I've been able to do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.63,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to regret there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got what you deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:33.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what I deserved, that's a great way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.93,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I live for myself, all of my problems are my iown fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.68,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to hold a grudge against anyone, and absolutely no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.65,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think of it that way, I can take just about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.27,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep wasting food, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:56.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be my dad's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:00.39,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was too honest. Too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:06.96,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Every morning reading the paper, the worries of the world brought him to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:14.95,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad believed that to create a new era, a new faith was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:20.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So his sermons at time strayed beyond the dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:24.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And as time passed, his flock became fewer and fewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was excommunicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.46,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one would listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It all seems so obvious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When outsiders looked at it, all they saw was a weird cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:43.33,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how just or how obvious his teachings were, society made him an outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:49.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our family was left with nothing, not even food to put on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.07,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.32,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad had said nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just talked about different things than other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:05.99,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had just lent him their ears, even for five minutes, anyone could've understood that he was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:11.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one would listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.17,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurt. I hated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:20.43,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stand that no one understood him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.10,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked Kyubey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:28.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asked him to make everyone listen seriously to my Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:35.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning, the pews were packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:40.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, more worshippers arrived with an unnatural vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I joined the ranks of the magical girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:51.07,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how just Dad's sermons, they wouldn't destroy witches on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:56.80,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt my chance had come, and rushed headstrong into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:01.84,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Dad and I would be heads and tails of the saving-the-world coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then my Dad found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:16.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he learned that his flock was driven not by faith but by magic, he snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:21.91,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He called his own daughter a witch sent to tempt men's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:28.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so ironic! I spent every night {\i1}fighting{\fscx40} {\r} witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.08,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.08,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His end was miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:42.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drowning his sorrows in drink, driven in the end to madness, he led his family to a pointless suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish destroyed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:59.88,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a wish without thinking of anyone else's circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.70,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and it resulted in misfortune for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:08.91,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I swore within my heart that I would never use magic for the sake of another again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:14.05,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That I would use all this power for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:23.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A wish is no idle matter. For every beam of hope you pray for, a shadow of despair is cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:28.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That way it's a zero-sum game. The balance of the world is preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get serious and focus on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Live how you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:45.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it. You talk about living for your own sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:48.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but here you are worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.66,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You made the same mistake in the beginning that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:58.25,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to keep living like this. You'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:02.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already paid too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:07.01,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not get some change back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.72,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:17.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know what I'm doing, so I just can't stand watching you muddle through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.38,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.74,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:31.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't regret wishing for someone else's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:35.48,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided I'll never regret it. I don't want to make what I felt then a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.61,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.54,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:43.37,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I paid too dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:48.86,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This power can do so many amazing things if used the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:56.29,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did you even get this apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you pay the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.49,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell me, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.24,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't eat that apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.02,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even be happy it was offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! We're magical girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else we can rely on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue fighting, following my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:30.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get in your way, you can try and kill me again, but I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.06,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.28,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a little under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.81,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:26.69,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.45,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's really—-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kamijo was released?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.80,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all healed up now, Kamijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.59,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Being cooped up in my house won't do my rehab any good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to get me walking without a crutch by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.94,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka, you haven't even talked to him yet. Go say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.11,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.42,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:34.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been keeping a secret from you and Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.98,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been fond of Kyosuke Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:55.50,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Hitomi, I didn't think you had it in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:58.26,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Kyosuke, such a ladykiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.62,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're his childhood friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:07.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I guess, I mean, I'm kinda stuck with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.13,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:16.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind. I'm not going to lie to myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.14,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:22.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you face your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.27,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:32.78,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my dear friend, so I don't want to steal your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:40.05,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had your eye on him for longer than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:44.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sio you have the right to preempt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.48,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.79,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, after school, I will confess my love to Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:59.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait a day. Sayaka, make sure in that time that you have no regrets about not telling Kamijo how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.67,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.77,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:38.43,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:44.68,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why are you so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.61,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a regret today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:02.58,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a moment, I thought that if I hadn't saved Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.47,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worthy of being an ally of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.79,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even look Mami in the face like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.90,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi's taking Kyosuke away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:28.96,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead! I'm just a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:32.53,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never embrace him like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.76,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never tell him "kiss me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:54.35,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.75,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.51,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now. I just needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.23,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go hunt us some witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.07,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting you to just sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.63,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fighting a witch today, not a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.83,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna drop a Grief Seed, so it's not a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising that that would make you back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.89,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot's messing up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.97,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:40.48,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.57,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stand back! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.44,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you how this is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.67,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:49.70,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way. I'm doing this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.34,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.15,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:18.85,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:26.36,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't want to, I don't have to feel a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:34.55,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Please, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:07.73,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:09.31,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:10.22,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:10.67,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:13.52,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting, adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:15.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an adult game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:16.60,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:17.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katherine!{let's see who complains about this being a typo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:17.64,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:25.57,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a different kind of magical girl than you lot. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:31.08,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need no reward. I'll never use magic for my own benefit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:34.17,madoka-dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been such a fool.
